      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "W / A / S / D To Movement\n\nMouse Click | Sowing the Seeds\n\nSelect
    a seed from your inventory and click on an empty slot to begin your harvest.\n\nSelected
    Slot + Click | Botanical Strike\n\nTo initiate a Vegetable Attack, select your
    desired plant from the hotbar and click on the battlefield to deploy your leafy
    defenses.\n\n[ I ] Key | Inventory Access\n\nOpen your Knapsack to manage your
    resources, gear, and collected loot.\n\nNumber Keys [ 1 \u2013 9 ] | Quick Select\n\nSwiftly
    toggle through your Action Slots to choose the right tool or plant for the moment."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 78349aa955b2fe447bceeb0e87f6749a, type: 2}
